===Etymology===
From {{bor|en|fa-cls|اَفْغَانِسْتَان}}, from {{m|fa-cls|اَفْغَان|t=Afghan}} + {{m|fa-cls|ـِسْتَان|t=[[-istan]]: [[land]] of}},<ref name=OED>{{R:OED Online|Afghanistanism|''n.'', Etymology|1164431169|date=July 2023|noformat=1}}</ref> equivalent to {{af|en|Afghan|-i-|-stan}}.

